293
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,620
The Gu family has a project starting

294
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,120
with a funding gap

295
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,790
of about 50 million.

296
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:09,040
Consider it a wedding gift.

297
00:17:09,910 --> 00:17:11,120
To me,

298
00:17:11,450 --> 00:17:12,620
she's worth that much.

299
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:19,410
You're so generous.

300
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:21,160
I'm sure Mrs. Sheng

301
00:17:21,370 --> 00:17:23,200
will never forget it.

302
00:17:29,850 --> 00:17:34,430
