330
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,660
Ye Si did.

331
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:50,540
I...

332
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,370
I'll talk to her.

333
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:53,910
It doesn't matter.

334
00:19:54,870 --> 00:19:57,200
