337
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:01,790
Yes, yes.

338
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,620
You're absolutely right.

339
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:04,870
Mr. Xu,

340
00:20:06,660 --> 00:20:07,790
Editor Gu

341
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:09,910
is so professional and sharp.

342
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,290
It's a blessing

343
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:13,660
for your magazine to have her.

344
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:15,910
I know, right?

345
00:20:16,950 --> 00:20:18,410
Lanshan has

346
00:20:18,410 --> 00:20:21,370
always been our gem.

347
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,330
She's the best!

348
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:24,450
Mr. Sheng,

349
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:25,700
