351
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,500
Take care, Mr. Sheng!

352
00:20:40,620 --> 00:20:42,250
Good thing you didn't ask.

353
00:20:42,660 --> 00:20:43,700
Great.

354
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,120
Ye Si!

355
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:05,580
Let's go home.

356
00:21:07,250 --> 00:21:08,120
No need.

357
00:21:25,290 --> 00:21:31,670
♪In a flash, back to the past♪

358
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:33,770
