365
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:07,870
It will take two to three months

366
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,000
to recover,

367
00:22:09,290 --> 00:22:10,620
and at least six months

368
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:12,370
before trying to conceive again.

369
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:13,870
You need to be careful

370
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,200
during this time.

371
00:22:16,290 --> 00:22:17,370
I understand.

372
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:20,700
Don't tell Papa Sheng.

373
00:22:22,290 --> 00:22:23,450
Don't let anyone else know,

374
00:22:23,540 --> 00:22:24,870
especially him.

375
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:27,330
Please keep it a secret.

376
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:29,250
Please, Uncle Wang.

377
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:32,540
Just this once.

378
00:22:32,790 --> 00:22:33,790
Never again.

379
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,040
Okay.

380
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:36,620
I'll leave now.

381
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:38,830
Thanks, Uncle Wang.

382
00:22:50,950 --> 00:22:51,950
Chu,

383
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:54,250
I'm sorry.

384
00:22:56,370 --> 00:22:58,330
