389
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,790
Why did you do this?

390
00:23:10,330 --> 00:23:12,580
I'll do anything

391
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:14,950
to make you happy.

392
00:23:15,450 --> 00:23:16,450
Okay?

393
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,080
When you wake up,

394
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,750
I'll give you this card.

395
00:23:24,290 --> 00:23:28,350
♪Cross the line, it's you and me♪

396
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:31,910
♪Softly saying goodbye, set free♪

397
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:35,410
Mr. Sheng,

398
00:23:35,950 --> 00:23:36,910
you said

399
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:38,950
we'd change the terms.

400
00:23:39,410 --> 00:23:40,830
Don't forget that.

401
00:23:42,450 --> 00:23:43,500
Okay?

402
00:23:46,350 --> 00:23:50,140
♪I don't want to give up yet♪

403
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,450
Alright.

404
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:54,870
As you wish.

405
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:57,220
♪But your trail I can't detect♪

406
00:23:57,220 --> 00:24:01,890
♪You've gone, no trace left♪

407
00:24:01,890 --> 00:24:05,640
♪Through the crowd, I hug you tight♪

408
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:09,970
