419
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:30,970
Mr. Lu!

420
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,470
Mr. Sheng.

421
00:24:34,270 --> 00:24:35,020
Sheng Shi,

422
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:36,140
are you messing with me?

423
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:39,970
Mr. Lu,

424
00:24:40,890 --> 00:24:42,430
that's really rude,

425
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:44,180
