426
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,140
Business is like war.

427
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,430
You should know this.

428
00:24:48,470 --> 00:24:49,310
Also,

429
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,770
wins and losses are part of the game.

430
00:24:52,430 --> 00:24:54,430
Acting so frantic

431
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,930
isn't a good look.

432
00:24:58,220 --> 00:24:59,180
You should know,

433
00:24:59,390 --> 00:25:00,390
that actions like this

434
00:25:00,930 --> 00:25:02,560
have consequences.

435
00:25:04,850 --> 00:25:05,810
Alright.

436
00:25:09,060 --> 00:25:10,600
We're done here.

437
00:25:11,350 --> 00:25:12,060
I have to get to

438
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:14,140
the Han family's engagement party.

439
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:22,430
See Mr. Lu out.

440
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:23,270
Yes.

441
00:25:27,020 --> 00:25:28,640
Mr. Lu, please.

442
00:25:29,970 --> 00:25:32,100
The Han and Sheng families,

443
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:34,680
I won't spare either of you.

444
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,970
I never wanted to do this!

445
00:25:49,390 --> 00:25:50,270
Wait for me!

446
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:57,310
En, you look amazing today.

447
00:25:57,520 --> 00:25:59,220
The most beautiful bride in the world.

448
00:25:59,390 --> 00:26:00,430
You're such a sweet talker.

449
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:04,310
Here's a gift for you.

450
00:26:04,850 --> 00:26:05,810
Congratulations on your engagement.

451
00:26:05,930 --> 00:26:07,350
