455
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,680
but it matches with mine.

456
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:17,180
It's the thought that counts.

457
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:18,180
Thanks, Shan.

458
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,100
I love it.

459
00:26:19,180 --> 00:26:20,100
Help me put it on.

460
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:23,600
Shan,

461
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:25,810
