let me and Chengchi know.

471
00:26:40,930 --> 00:26:42,770
We'll handle him.

472
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:44,310
Don't worry,

473
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:45,350
he wouldn't dare.

474
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,100
Let me help you with the bracelet.

475
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:52,390
It looks nice.

476
00:26:56,890 --> 00:26:57,850
Lanshan,

477
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,640
come with me.

478
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,640
I'll be right back.

479
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:12,220
Make sure the balloons

480
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:13,140
are arranged nicely,

481
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:14,390
different sizes apart

482
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:15,310
for a better look.

483
00:27:15,390 --> 00:27:16,270
Mr. Han.

484
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,520
- Here, too.
- Is there

485
00:27:18,520 --> 00:27:20,060
