486
00:27:20,970 --> 00:27:21,680
Yes, when I checked this morning...

487
00:27:21,770 --> 00:27:24,220
He is so romantic.

488
00:27:24,930 --> 00:27:26,810
No wonder Chengchi and En

489
00:27:26,930 --> 00:27:28,850
have been so sweet for years.

490
00:27:29,890 --> 00:27:31,220
Does romance even work?

491
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,560
Of course, it does.

492
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:33,680
Haven't you

493
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,890
