494
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,720
You should try it sometime.

495
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:39,770
Be romantic.

496
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,470
Mom.

497
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,310
You really dressed up.

498
00:27:57,060 --> 00:27:58,680
Trying to outshine En?

499
00:27:59,140 --> 00:28:00,060
No, I'm not.

500
00:28:01,850 --> 00:28:02,810
Let me warn you.

501
00:28:03,180 --> 00:28:04,680
Today is En's big day.

502
00:28:04,970 --> 00:28:06,350
Don't try anything funny.

503
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:08,390
If I hadn't seen

504
00:28:08,390 --> 00:28:10,020
