512
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:23,720
Mom,

513
00:28:23,890 --> 00:28:25,970
I sincerely wish them the best.

514
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:28,640
I've never had any improper thoughts.

515
00:28:28,970 --> 00:28:30,060
You'd better not.

516
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:36,890
Ji Lang!

517
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,520
